&gt;(Frank Ramsey, Tyler Cowen)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + future_humans_matter_with_discounting&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Future people are inside the circle, but with a positive pure-time discount rate — the moderate longtermist position. A modest discount is enough to keep present, measurable global health competitive with future-protecting work; remove it (the next assumption) and the astronomical numbers take over. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylVmFz4jYQ%2FSs7mXYKNCEGksuFDh8IkEvmuF6GpL3phAwR9hqrkSWPJMfhcvnvXdkQIJg2M%2FUXjHf37e5b6UnPewGGLBW2pwLca%2B8dHkKn04EbzbgEq8DX7PucXjIJ47TpNY4gU1oEjxwzyBqT5qQFFWNVAq2qCxxLAugak8aJ5UqCHxFOGzxImFZ%2BxJlwMI3TJjQgZHrCMjafRGnMpFkamsAkj5kwE6NizCJml5YWhKlNNS4CJjGzFvUk4zaaBNz4KpWWy1lew4D5EbBVIdwAg6u5jeg95AKB2luZzSFYl4gFgdkHjcQJl2hA6RxM4wHVz2KkdNzQdxth0dovhmqSfo7xG%2FgqTpShElYOFCsDJET6xE2OZiyTARNKIsREuqjD%2FSung8d7V6oLx6cEfUuBj0ykCCrMEVb013OwMzQWpukcUpfGBRpcb6wNN4R14QhDGCKbpVgEfhr8Phh1bwZ9mM5hhhI1s1hP5ssxY8DtBkM1Mu6DVLaow5FISDlWn2sqFTAM3Q8xjI59pWdET6JpmHoOU0oRcp%2FT%2Bz6cDc6%2FjgbUvmYiR8iQzyI3PCJDKLfwIn5fDE2omVSaFgScej9D7xIqSlOrByo8iNlMcpsGCGdfbwa9KtVjVJp85taPUPaZmF%2Bh%2FsME0IHnsQRIUCUCL1AkGLxavLp37BJ69WPnk6EQU6RKPtH0HETh4jUKH6%2FhnPKlhjpkvk2ZOGPy4c98SM61tSNTrQS6BpUGHOyCq47ly1jOgo1GXC3e0aIYrzmWLA63HFqLjrwmlct4vOWw7KZJPdtIbNgb9aazHp0Qm1myaWp6nrOdHFERY5lxEUzTmdn0%2BVD4fGzmPkyIEIOSWXRnmvskPCmtgR6zzFitkgjJq4eSvi6Jby1Kzacj%2BCOaa%2FaYs9pXQjB9Ga5FFzF5%2FU3nHxR5hzx0ppaXZ%2B7xRy74d%2BbW9UAGbiAEK7dglusiHzlt%2FIfriGkcYazW87uW8aCR90wv3qnzLoTKdW269tqyBwfZ8FZP7u29ed7JS%2B2%2FaahtdP7r%2B1DfQ0ztX4iolbSdL2GSv0ypkkXwNCKwEQapv01oa0Foo%2Fn%2FCC3PsbPW4vS4zfrd4V9ADGsnwQlJ60937XVdCzY0z%2FJ4cSysNM1XZCTFI37fSDeFszdnJCSpNU46uXUq5it3ZHTg1nXwDLTJsQ3jvaHySQedxsFDIXLjvX3Igldi2xAjk5VSFaxS0w142d%2BEdBMu9FvMy8HWBWg3xjcSN3AXAWpHczuHSvfLebUccUOyyiG7l1%2FgEHoLrIG0GhM6SjHVJuLJDth1oSuH3ToMy5E2JNEhOf3xjk8%2BbiNeR3TAJUDt030G4Uqrv4nLHWNZl9McdgvuG0kq3U0MYRioREWpCR3ytJACNDsI3RbicvTucHg%2B6O9g741Q5wSSnn0omQ0YFqKb8ajY2TCiawfTfrSjvi0BWJV357acpiPPXZs6MOTG1jXSvjNYyf8Ype3ZvFJsiX14%2FvH0A57qazleqnRQTt09qAMLoFvvbrGTb0pvUjcXl9er7diG%2FJbJifHp8jpFG51TFYY249rljDI4j%2FXsY7n38g%2F3TdQO" id="w1_2_3"><mxCell style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=11;fillColor=#f2e3b3;strokeColor=#c9a72a;fontColor=#57450e;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="662" y="0" width="222" height="108" as="geometry"/></mxCell></object><object label="No pure-time discount&lt;br&gt;(astronomical stakes)&lt;br&gt;[1+2+3+4]&lt;br&gt;→ AI safety (Redwood Research)&lt;br&gt;▼ 23 more worldviews" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + no_discounting_future_humans&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Accept that future people count exactly as much as present ones (Ord, MacAskill) and Bostrom&#x27;s astronomical-waste argument follows: the expected size of the future dwarfs the present, and reducing existential risk dominates everything measurable. This is the stop Ajeya Cotra&#x27;s near-termist deliberately gets off before. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 4 no_discounting_future_humans" link="https://viewer.diagrams.net/?lightbox=1&amp;nav=1&amp;chrome=0#Uhttps%3A%2F%2Fraw.githubusercontent.com%2Fmorganrivers%2Ftrain_to_crazy_town%2Fmain%2Fdiagram%2Ftrain_tree__w1_2_3_4.drawio" id="w1_2_3_4"><mxCell style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=11;fillColor=#f6e0c0;strokeColor=#c9932a;fontColor=#5a3f10;dashed=1;dashPattern=8 4;strokeWidth=3;fontStyle=1;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="474" y="239" width="244" height="108" as="geometry"/></mxCell></object><object label="Animals matter a lot&lt;br&gt;(RP welfare ranges)&lt;br&gt;[1+2+3+5]&lt;br&gt;→ Shrimp Welfare Project&lt;br&gt;(Bob Fischer, Brian Tomasik)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + animals_matter_a_lot&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Replace the neuron-count proxy with Rethink Priorities&#x27; welfare-range estimates (Fischer et al.) and count invertebrates — shrimp, insects, and the ~10^19 soil animals. Under RP medians a chicken&#x27;s welfare range is a third of a human&#x27;s, not a fiftieth, and wild/soil invertebrates carry significant aggregate (nematode) weight, so invertebrate work dominates. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 5 animals_matter_a_lot" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylVmFz4jYQ%2FSs7mXZKKCHGJHcNHT4QQi6Zcr0Mob3phAwR9hqrkSWPJMfhcvnvXdmQQDBtZuovGGv1dvet9q2e9kKMWCZsX4W419k7PIRutwtjzbgEqyDQ7NuCXnIJk8z3WkeQKy3CB4455K2pP21Pj6FmrErheN9tnUiC6BmTJanlSkIQE1IHPEiZVkHMmXBArRMfWhAxPWU5W0zjLGHSrBZ8YJInTJipUQnmMbOrlTZEmc00LjdME2Yt6mnObTwNuQlUJi2X85X58QvQ0pBNhbJFhAMWxMBew%2BQGGFwtbEzvERcIlP7rsjkE68JgYWgaoJE44xINKF2AaTyg7FiC5IMb%2Bm5jLBP%2FyVDEMigwfoVAJakyLsAXA9orQyRE%2BsRNgWYskyETSiIkVBTRhLsXzgcPdy5Utx0fUwwsbXxgIkNQUYHwWp5mAXaKxsIsW0Dm3LiNBtcT68B1rHmSwlcUVA6EK63%2BJtxy96fB74NRbzw4g9kC5ihRM4vNdLE6Cxhyu0FTnRYbIJUtg3FMElKBdcY14QJGkfshmtGVQOk5cZRSCEwvYEYuIh5wem%2FA6eD8y2hAHGgmCoQc%2BTx29SVGhHKnM%2BZ3ZeWEmkulqdRw4v0I%2FUuoKU35HqjoIGFzyW0WIpx%2BGQ%2F6%2BxSPUVn6G7dBjPKMicUV6j9MCF14mkiAFFUq8AJFiuHLitf0jp1Dr3nsbHIUYoYUyScqoYMoTbxWaeO1nFFxGlFHLLAZE6dM3v9ZVMqZtnd4qldA16HWgoNdcPsT%2BTyR83AjEReLd7QMxvMnkiXRlkF7mZHnU7iMJ1sGq2x8ytnGYmO91fTd6tFHYjNPN5d8z3NrH48oiInMuQhn2dxs2nwobX7xCxsmRIRhRS16c80DUqeMzkCfWWasVmmMZNVHSV9XxLeXoRbVEfwBzTV7KFg9U0IwfRmt7S73FPH7zj4s%2FQ555JbaXuG5zx%2B44N%2BYO9cDGbqCEKzcglmdi6Lk1P331zG10QgTte7fpYwHrSJnevFOnHWpZS5r07PXlt07yJb3%2BhTW3pvnnbzU%2F5uG%2BkbmP78P9T3E1P%2BFiHpF2sURJg3Mlao4BI8jAhthmAXbhLaXhLb8%2F0dotY%2BdsZYj5CY%2F6w3%2FAmJYOx1OSV9%2FuO2s61q4oXmWJ8vZ8KppgaJFUjzi941%2B03b2ZoxCmlnjpJM7faZx5%2BZGF25cBk9ATY4dmOwNVUA66DQO7kuRm%2Bw1IA9fiO1AgkzWKlVwn5JuwXNjE9JVuNRvsagGWxeg3