%2FAFYYD2Y%3D" id="w1_2_3_5_6_7_8"><mxCell style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=11;fillColor=#e9b0a0;strokeColor=#b8402a;fontColor=#511810;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1224" y="1195" width="244" height="108" as="geometry"/></mxCell></object><object label="Count soil animals&lt;br&gt;(~10^19 nematodes)&lt;br&gt;[1+2+3+5+6+7+8+11]&lt;br&gt;→ Shrimp Welfare Project&lt;br&gt;(Vasco Grilo)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + animals_matter_a_lot + suffering_focused + meat_eater_problem + net_negative_animal_lives + soil_animals&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Grilo&#x27;s soil-animal accounting: ~10^19 soil nematodes, mites and springtails dominate the welfare effects of almost anything. Global-health charities raise food demand and cropland (~137 m^2-yr/$ for GiveWell top charities, ~1.11 kQALY/$ of soil-animal welfare change); with soil lives net-negative, the arithmetic makes GiveWell&#x27;s top charities net-harmful. Only enters once invertebrates already count, so it requires animals_matter_a_lot. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 5 animals_matter_a_lot → 6 suffering_focused → 7 meat_eater_problem → 8 net_negative_animal_lives → 11 soil_animals" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylVn9v4kYQ%2FSqjqFUJTYhtkvCj4g9CuLuoXO9E0lbVcfIt9hhvs961dtchXC7fvbM2EAjQnlQkhPHMvpl5M%2Ft2n45iTFgh7EDFeNQ9OjuDXq8Hd5pxCVZBpNnXBT3MJUyKwPPPYa60iB84zmHuh0HYDC%2FCy7AVtkPfh5qxKgffP3YgE0lgfWOKLLdcSYhSwuyCBznTKko5Ew7S7wTgQ8J0yOZsEaZFxqRZGQJgkmdMmNCoDOcpsytLE5LCFhqXC8KMWYs6nHObhjE3kSqk5XK2cr9YAy0dWSjUGuwSTJEkqGlBmKioMBivTC3IkNmQvrQo12oqMFvZ2iDRhhJnzPIHDKsIoaDndQHEiVFcLG2mpGTIohTYCy%2FcAIOPC5vSc8IFAjH%2FYjZnYF3dLI7NCWikdnFJAZQuwTSeEp0sQ8qPG3pvU6yY%2FskQRTIqMX6BSGW5Mo6RtQOtlTESIr3iVWrGMhkzoSRCRvMgGvBl3e7hwxeXqluOjzlGlhY%2BMFEgqKREeJmMRgl2hcbCtFhA4cK4hQY3C%2BvCbap5lsOfKKj%2FCB%2B1%2Bptwq9Vvh78Nx%2F274TVMFzBDiZpa0MgX