l animals&lt;br&gt;(~10^19 nematodes)&lt;br&gt;[1+2+3+5+6+8+11]&lt;br&gt;→ Shrimp Welfare Project&lt;br&gt;(Vasco Grilo)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + animals_matter_a_lot + suffering_focused + net_negative_animal_lives + soil_animals&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Grilo&#x27;s soil-animal accounting: ~10^19 soil nematodes, mites and springtails dominate the welfare effects of almost anything. Global-health charities raise food demand and cropland (~137 m^2-yr/$ for GiveWell top charities, ~1.11 kQALY/$ of soil-animal welfare change); with soil lives net-negative, the arithmetic makes GiveWell&#x27;s top charities net-harmful. Only enters once invertebrates already count, so it requires animals_matter_a_lot. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 5 animals_matter_a_lot → 6 suffering_focused → 8 net_negative_animal_lives → 11 soil_animals" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylVm1z4jYQ%2Fis7mXYKNCG2yQvQ4QMh3F2mXO%2BGpO10jhufsNdYjSx5JDmEy%2BW%2Fd2UDgQDtzZQvUbyrZ3efXT3S01GMCSuEHagYj7pHp6fQ6%2FXgTjMuwSqINPu6oMVcwqQIPP8M5kqL%2BIHjHOZ%2BGISt8Dy8CNuh70PNWJWD79cdxEQSVN%2BYIsstVxKilBC74EHOtIpSzoQD9DsB%2BJAwHbI5W4RpkTFpVoYAmOQZEyY0KsN5yuzK0oKksIXG5YYwY9aiDufcpmHMTaQKabmcrdzP10BLRxYKtQa7AFMkCWraECYqKgzGK1MbJNpQ4oxZ%2FoBhhRIKWq%2BTpLqN4mJpM2XZQxalwF5q5wYYfFzYlNYJFwjE7YvZnIJ1tbE4NsegkRrCJQVQugTTeEKUsQwpcW7ou02xYvMnQzTIqMT4BSKV5cq4qtcOtFfGSIj0iVepGctkzISSCBl1XDThy7qhw4cvLlW3HR9zjCxtfGCiQFBJifDS%2B2YJdoXGwrRYQOHCuI0GNwvrwm2qeZbDnyioxwgftfqbcKvdb4e%2FDcf9u%2BE1TBcwQ4maWWzmi9WgYcztFk0NMh6DpM6VyTgmCanEuuaacAGpj%2FSHaEbXAqVnxFFOKTC9gCmFSHjEaX0MV8M3H8ZD4kAzUSLMkc9SNzTEiFBu9FP%2BpeqcUDOpNHUXOt6PMLiBmtJU74lKTjI2k9wWMcLVh7vhoE75GFXkv3IbpSivmVh8RP27iaEHTxMJkKPKBb5DkWO8tnhN79wF9JrnzmeOQkyRMnlLLXQQlYvnVz6e75zKEUedsMgWTFwxef9H2Snn2joQqbEHugE1H04OwdUn8nkiZ%2FFWIS4X72yZjBdMJMuSHYfWsiIvoHQZz3YcVtUEVLNNxZbdbwbOenZJbM7zbVPgec52eUZJTOS