s are not worth living. Reducing that suffering is worth more per dollar (you are mitigating a catastrophe, not improving a good life), most of all for the astronomical wild-invertebrate populations. Combined with the meat-eater problem it drives human charities firmly net-negative — every human sustained means more net-negative farmed lives. Presupposes counting wild/invertebrate animals, so it requires animals_matter_a_lot; and like the meat-eater problem it is a near-term animal get-off point, not combined with astronomical-stakes longtermism (no_discounting_future_humans). || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 5 animals_matter_a_lot → 7 meat_eater_problem → 8 net_negative_animal_lives" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylVmFv4kYQ%2FSujqFWBJsQ2BBIqPhDC3UXleieStqqOk2%2Bxx3ib9a61uw7hcvnvnbUhgQDtSUVCGM%2Fsm5k3s2%2F38SjGhBXCDlWMR72j01Po9%2FtwqxmXYBVEmn1d0sNCwrQIPL8NC6VFfM9xAQs%2FDMJWeBZ2w3OoGatyOK%2B75VNJMANjiiy3XEmIUkLrgQc50ypKORMOzL8IwIeE6ZAt2DJMi4xJszYEwCTPmDChURkuUmbXlhYkhS00rhaEGbMWdbjgNg1jbiJVSMvlfO1%2B9gy0cmShUM9gXciQ2ZC%2BZMm1mgnM1rZzkGhDiXNm%2BT2GFUwo6NmUBY5YlAJ7qZIbYPBxaVN6TrhAIAZfzOYUrKuCxbE5Bo1EO5doQOkSTOMJkcMypES4ofc2xYq3nwwVLKMS4xeIVJYr4%2Bp7dqC1MkZCpFe8Ss1YJmMmlETIqK%2BiCV%2Be2za6%2F%2BJSdcvxIcfI0sJ7JgoElZQILx1ulmCXaCzMiiUULoxbaHCzsB7cpJpnOfyJgrqJ8FGrvwm3Wv129NtoMrgdXcFsCXOUqInrZr5cjxPG3G7R1CDjMUjqUZmMY5KQSqwrrgkXMEncD9GMrgVKz4mjnFJgegkzCpHwiNPzMVyO3nyYjIgDzUSJsEA%2BT914ECNCuQFP%2BZeqc0LNpdLUYrjwfoThNdSUpnpPVHKSsbnktogRLj%2FcjoZ1yseoIv%2BV2yhFecXE8iPq300MfXicSoAcVS7wHYoc42eL1%2FTOXECveeZ8FijEDCmTt9RCB1G5eH7l4%2FnOqRxm1AmLbMHEJZN3f5Sdcq6tA5Eae6AbUPPh5BBcfSqfpnIebxXicvHaq2S8YCpZluw4tFYVeQGly3i247CuJqCabSq27H4zcNZ2l9hc5NumwPOcrdumJKZywUU8K%2BZm26dT%2BZwHpQ8TIsF4Ty8Gc80jEriCZmDILDNWqzxF8hqipLdr4lurVMvulLv8ht2XrF4pIZi%2BTjZWV2vK%2FAPnH1dxxzxxppZXRh7yey74V%2BbmeiRj1xCClTsw67koW067%2F%2B4mpW00wUxtxncl44lf1kwP3oXzrqTQVW0G9sayOwfpey%2Bf0tt79flOXhr%2FTUNjq%2FKfvw%2F1e4hp