problem it is a near-term animal get-off point, not combined with astronomical-stakes longtermism (no_discounting_future_humans). || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 5 animals_matter_a_lot → 8 net_negative_animal_lives" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylVmFv2zYQ%2FSuHYMMcL3FkO0kTD%2F7gOG4b1F0LJ1sx1IVKSyeLC0UKJBXFTfPfd6TsxI7lrcD8JYx4fHf3jveOD3sxJqwQdqhi3OvtHR1Bv9%2BHG824BKsg0uzbghalhGnRCdrHUCot4juOJZTtsBN2w5PwDBrGqhzO9t3hqSSQgTFFlluuJEQpYfUggJxpFaWcCQfVPu9AGxKmQ1ayRZgWGZNmtdEBJnnGhAmNyrBMmV3tdCEpbKFxeSDMmLWow5LbNIy5iVQhLZfzlfnJE9DSkIVCPYGdgUQbSpwzy%%2B4jVKUl0wsPqL%2Bw8TQh4epBMhR5QLfosgxftoJWsGJcxi0TpxNiULMkCJ5QyV0EJVJ0K5sgrYz8hcWdcIiWzBxweTtn75SzrS7w1OzBroJjTYc7oLbn8rHqZzHG4m4WILjZTBBZypZlmwZdJcZBR0Kl%2FFsy2CVTYdytqnY2G%2B3Om73%2BBWxWeabW50gcHuvjimIqSy5iGfF3GzanFY2Zx1vw4RIMK6pxWCueUQSVtAdGDLLjNUqT5Gshijp64r47jJUXx3f5dfszrN6qYRg%2BipZO12d8fF3nH1c%2BR3zxG11A%2B95yO%2B44N%2BYu9cjGbuCEKzcglndC19y6v7b65TaaIKZWvfvUsbDts%2BZFsG5s67kzmVtBvbaslsH2Q6ef946ePH7QV6a%2F01DcyPzX38M9UeIaf4LEc2atP0VJg0slaq5BPcTAptgXETbhHaXhLY7%2F4%2FQeh87Y61GyOfycjD%2BC4hh7XQ4J3396UtvXdfiDc2zPFvOhmdNixRtkuIRvy%2F0m46zF5MW8sIaJ53c6TNNRDc3%2BvDZZfAA1OTYg%2BneWEWkg07j4LYSueneAZTxE7E9yJDJRq0K7lPSbXg82IR0Fa70WyzqwdYFaDcGDRkB7jlB6WhuF9AYvH%2B9X4%2B4IVn1kIOr93AEwyXWSFqNOc1TLLRJeb4Ddl3o6mFvqEJv3RsEYYxsXmA90oYkOqSgdXp6vIVWP193lGRdSivI4Ly7BfmJJJUeKIZwDDTSKtScJj1dpBjNDkK3hXjp4WSb2PH49ehyB4EvtNpzSJJ2WlMeMCxBV%2BZJ1dwwoecH01G6I8QtDfAReuAvrus0TT33fOrDmBvb0kitZ7Dh%2FzFK24tFo%2BqKA3j4fv8d7ltrPh73aVbO3HuoD0ugz8GXZTPf1L6obt5eXT93ZA%2F8c5UT6bPVs4p6nVMUhvpx7ZFGHpzFuvep3Hv8B9uA7wU%3D" id="w1_2_3_5_8"><mxCell style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=11;fillColor=#e9b0a0;strokeColor=#b8402a;fontColor=#511810;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="384" y="1195" width="244" height="108" as="geometry"/></mxCell></object><object label="Count soil animals&lt;br&gt;(~10^19 nematodes)&lt;br&gt;[1+2+3+5+8+11]&lt;br&gt;→ Shrimp 