 creating happiness. Factory farming, malaria and the worst wild-animal conditions weigh up; speculative future-flourishing bets weigh down. Arises most naturally from taking animal suffering seriously, so it requires animals_somewhat. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 suffering_focused" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylVu9z4jYQ%2FVd2Mu0UaEJsyI%2BGDh8IkEvmuF6GpL3phAwn7DVWI0seSY7D5fK%2Fd2VDgADXzNRfMNbq7du30pOe90KMWCZsV4W419o7PIR2uw23mnEJVkGg2bcZveQSRlnD848gV1qEjxxzyP1xY9wcn0DFWJXCSdVNHUmC6BiTJanlSkIQE1ILPEiZVkHMmXBA%2FlkDfIiYHrOczcZxljBpFgMNYJInTJixUQnmMbOLkSZEmc00zieME2Yt6nHObTwOuQlUJi2X00X4CZgsilDTp3GkgsxgWNDrsyAGtuTIDTC4ntmY3iMuEKj25bA5BOs4sDA0%2B6CRBOMSDShdgGk8oNJYgsSEG%2FpuYyyr%2FsUQXRkUGL9DoJJUGcfuNYDmyhAJkT5xU6AZy2TIhJIICXVE1OHrq%2BD9x6%2BOqpuOTykGliY%2BMpEhqKhAWPamXoCdo7EwyWaQuTRuosHVwlpwS1iXTkuEAbJphuXED%2F0%2F%2BsPObb8HkxlMUaJmFuvpbLEGMOR2TaEaDe6DVLbk4UQkpAKrxzVRBaRG0A8pjE59packT6qpz3oGE0oR8YDT%2Bz6c9y8%2BD%2FtUvmaiQMiRT2PXVxJDKLcqY%2F61bJpQU6k0rRU4836G7hVUlKZSD1R0kLCp5DYLEc4%2F3%2Fa7VeJjVJZ%2B5DaIUfaYmF2j%2FtOE0IbnkQRIUaUCL1GkGL6OeHXv2CX06scuJkchJkhMPlD3HEQZ4vlljOe7oGIVoo5YYDMmzpl8%2BKtokgtt7shU2wJdg4oPB7vgqiP5MpLTcK0Qx8U7mpPxGiPJkmgjoDmvyGsQXcaTjYBFNQ2q2cZibdyvN9zo0SmpmafrQw3Pc2OnR0RiJHMuwkk2NesxJ2XMb40ihgkRYbilF52p5gG5UkZroMssM1arNEaK6qKkrwvhm3OqRXcEf0Rzwx4LVXtKCKavopXZ5ZyCf8PFh2XeAY%2FcUNMrMnf5Ixf8G3Prui9D1xCClRswi3VRtJw2%2FsNNzDQOMVGr%2BV3JeOAXNdOLd%2BaiSw9zVZuOvbHswUH63vIpor03zzt1qf23DLW1yn99H%2Bp7hKn9QIjalrKLJUz2lyu1ZRE8DQlsiGEWbAranAvqN%2F6foNtz7ORanh53ea8z%2BBtIYe0sOCVr%2Fem%2Btepr4ZrnWZ7Mj4WlpwWKBsnxSN831k3T2ZvjE9LMGmed3DoXC5Q7Mtpw5yp4Btrk2ILR3kAF5IPO4%2BChNLnR3j7k4auwLUiQycpWF6xS0WRP8LK%2FDup6XDq4mG2HW7WgH6F8IYMDd0%2BgkjS3M6h0Pl1Ut2Ou2ZYD3YTsXH2CQ%2BjOsfrSakzpOMVMm5inO2BXzW4X140jcTvWmjGWWP6xf9o82gC8iemUS4Hqp%2FsOwrVW%2F5CcO3qz6qkF6gbcF%2FJVuqAYwjBQiUumKZ30tJpCNDsU3XTj7eidweCi39sh3xu3LhpDpna6pTlgWISuycNye8OQ7h5MB%2FEOfhsusKR37%2FadpnPP3Z3aMODG1jXS5jNYKf4Ype35rFLui314%2Fv70HZ7qKzleqnRaTtxlqA1zoDvvfr6db7dep24vr26We7IFxS2Uk%2BKTxZ2KdjsnFoZ25MoNjTK4iNXsI7n38i%2Bwat7c" id="w1_2_3_6"><mxCell style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=11;fillColor=#f2ccc0;strokeColor=#c96a4a;fontColor=#5a2410;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="701" y="717" width="236" height="108" as="geometry"/></mxCell></object><object label="Meat-eater problem&lt;br&gt;(saved humans eat animals)&lt;br&gt;[1+2+3+6+7]&lt;br&gt;→ The Humane League&lt;br&gt;(Michael Dickens, Vasco Grilo)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + suffering_focused + meat_eater_problem&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The meat-eater problem: a dollar of human global health also buys decades of that person&#x27;s meat consumption, and factory farming it causes suffering the animal circle now counts. Each present-human org is charged an additive penalty — farmed-animal life-years caused per human DALY, times the suffering per factory-farmed life-year, times the animal&#x27;s welfare range. Under a heavy animal welfare range the penalty can exceed the human benefit, so saving human lives looks net-harmful. Only bites once animals count, so it requires animals_somewhat; and it is a near-term human-vs-animal get-off point, not combined with astronomical-stakes longtermism (no_discounting_future_humans), where x-risk dominates and the meat bookkeeping is moot. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 suffering_focused → 7 meat_eater_problem" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylVmFv4kYQ%2FSujqFWBJsSGJCRUfCCE3EXH9U4k7ak6Ttxij%2FE2611rdx2Hy%2BW%2Fd9aGAMG0JxUJYTyzb2bezL7dp4MQI5YJO1AhHnQPjo%2Bh1%2BvBnWZcglUQaPZtQQ%2B5hEnW8vwTyJUW4QPHHHJ%2F2pq2p2fTDtSMVSl06m7xRBJI35gsSS1XEoKYsLrgQcq0CmLOhIPyL1rgQ8T0lOVsMY2zhEmzMrSASZ4wYaZGJZjHzK4sbYgym2lcLpgmzFrU05zbeBpyE6hMWi7nK%2FczMFkUoaZX00gFmcFwZepAgsxO6UvrU61mApMi9SELYmDr%2FLkBBh